{"tid":2434698,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"曾偉雄: 民主派初選案非濫捕　抱濫捕想法人士是出於同情","createTime":"2021-03-05T16:46:33.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-05T17:24:19.000Z","uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"7ed40ab8e08d790b502a56bf800c6086eeecf3d2","tid":2434698,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T16:46:33.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】正在北京出席兩會會議的全國政協委員、警務處前處長曾偉雄認為，民主派初選案並非濫捕，有這種想法的人是出於同情。<br />\n<br />\n警務處前處長曾偉雄：「你說濫捕的意思就是，用感情來看警方有否濫捕。其實就很難說，如果你同情某一方，便覺得有（濫捕），如果你不同情，便覺得沒有，我覺得最重要，就是警方有沒有依法辦事。在執法層面上，在現時執法現象層面來看，我又看不到濫捕，如果你用感情來說，那就很難答你了。」<br />\n<br />\n對於歐美國家禁售武器予香港警隊，曾偉雄指，警隊在使用有關武器時，較歐美更加克制，反問有關的制裁是基於專業的判斷還是政治考量。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=426341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D426341&d=sOSR1epLEapJbLCvIyWedRs8Bcr99949gko4GmpRTno%3D&h=6c22caae\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D426341&h=75bdbace\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=426341</a>"},{"pid":"5b6eef0838bef03d5e4b5da758c9af29ec012520","tid":2434698,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T16:48:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77f971767dd85b6a08eb41a768831ca6335cb104","tid":2434698,"uid":14422,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T16:52:41.000Z","msg":"咁納粹德國嘅蓋世太寶都係依法根據《紐倫堡法案》去逮捕猶太人，完全冇濫捕其他非猶太人。只不過係其他人同情猶太人姐"},{"pid":"156b0d9710547f94a32bc83755e532e80ba81a08","tid":2434698,"uid":2054,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T16:53:30.000Z","msg":"黑警死全家"},{"pid":"1fb7246457d629e2ffc1a2d5311e9a6651c1ccad","tid":2434698,"uid":14422,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score"